      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration (static compression-bending per ASTM F1717) at ambient laboratory conditions. Only one test condition was evaluated; the required level calls for at least two distinct loading configurations or environmental conditions to characterize model behavior across the COU envelope. This shortfall is acknowledged; the single-condition dataset limits confidence in extrapolation beyond the tested configuration."
