    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the FEA modeling framework achieves sufficient credibility for the intended COU. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achievedLevel 2 vs. requiredLevel 3) is considered acceptable given that the tested configuration directly replicates the regulatory submission scenario and all quantitative acceptance criteria for output comparison are satisfied. The overall assurance level is declared Medium, consistent with Model Risk Level 3 and the balanced evidence base.",
